Books and papers that we reference in comments of the source code.

[wend2005] Holger Wendland. ‘Scattered Data Approximation’. Nr. 17 of
           Cambridge Monographs on Applied and Computational Mathematics.
           Cambridge University Press 2005. ISBN: 978-0-521-84335-5.
           
[gstv2010] Fred G. Gustavson, Fred G. Gustavson, Jerzy Waśniewski,
           Jack J. Dongarra, and Julien Langou. ‘Rectangular Full Packed
           Format for Cholesky’s Algorithm: Factorization, Solution, and
           Inversion’.
           In: ACM Transactions on Mathematical Software 37.2 (April 2010)
           DOI: 10.1145/1731022.1731028